                <h2>How it works</h2>
                <span class="center-line"></span>
                <p class="sub-text margin40">
                    Karmency is 3D-printed currency designed to be passed around to thank people for random acts of kindness. On this site, you can <strong><a href="/coins/lookup">look up</a></strong> your Karmency Coin to see its history, tell the world how you got it, or let us know why you passed it on. You can also download a 3D model of a new coin and print your own!
